      <title>欧洲央行行长施纳贝尔淡化与美国政策分歧的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/ecb-s-schnabel-downplays-prospect-of-policy-divergence-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会委员伊莎贝尔·施纳贝尔淡化了欧元区利率路径与美国利率路径明显不同的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/ecb-s-schnabel-downplays-prospect-of-policy-divergence-from-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 16:55:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国批准房地美购买第二笔抵押贷款试点计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/us-approves-freddie-mac-pilot-program-to-buy-second-mortgages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国监管机构已批准房地产巨头房地美（Freddie Mac）开展一项购买二次抵押贷款的试点计划，这一转变最终可能降低家庭以房屋净值作为抵押的贷款成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/us-approves-freddie-mac-pilot-program-to-buy-second-mortgages</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 16:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Archegos Trader 倒闭数月后在圣特罗佩打马球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/archegos-trader-played-polo-in-st-tropez-months-after-collapse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Archegos Capital Management 于 2021 年 3 月倒闭后的那个夏天，前首席交易员 William Tomita 前往法国圣特罗佩，在那里他打马球并与朋友聚会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/archegos-trader-played-polo-in-st-tropez-months-after-collapse</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 16:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车需求放缓，巴斯夫退出 26 亿美元镍项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/basf-to-exit-2-6-billion-nickel-smelter-project-in-indonesia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于电动汽车销售增长放缓，巴斯夫公司计划停止与 Eramet SA 合作在印度尼西亚投资高达 26 亿美元建设镍钴精炼厂的项目，从而扭转了对这个东南亚国家的专项投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/basf-to-exit-2-6-billion-nickel-smelter-project-in-indonesia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 16:15:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
