      <title>高利率能持续多久？债券市场称可能永远如此</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/how-long-will-high-rates-last-bond-markets-say-maybe-forever</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在投资者对美国国债即将开始上涨的乐观情绪日益高涨时，债券市场的一项关键指标却向那些想要入市的人发出了令人担忧的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/how-long-will-high-rates-last-bond-markets-say-maybe-forever</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
